This falls under the category of systems and control (cs.SY). The use of linear approximations and the best linear approximation framework suggests a focus on machine learning and optimization (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The paper also mentions the use of neural networks and other nonlinear system identification approaches, which are relevant to neural networks (cs.NE) and social and information networks (cs.SI).
